Global users for our application.

Unicast IP(one serevr holds one ip) || anycast IP(all servers hold the same ip and the client is routed to the nearest one):

the concept of edge location to interact in a private aws netwrok.

2 ANYCAST IP are created for the application.

Works with Elastic IP, ec2 instances, ALB, NLB, public or private.

CloudFront: 
  for cacheable content(images/videos)
  Dynamic content

Global accelerator(newer):
  for wide range of applications over TCP or UDP.
  static IP addresses.
  for gaming(UDP), IoT(MQTT), 
  fast regional failover
  
  
